
Allow the user to input digits, afterward sort and print them in numerical order.

constrants:
1.we have to add digits.
2.print them in order

steps:

1. input which accept numbers not text
2. store the number in a place
3. do operation to find the smallest to greatest
4. save to the new place 
5. display it on webpage

INITIALIZE input as input 
INITIALIZE my number as empty array
INITIALIZE display as display
<!-- access the value of input and store it to the array -->
array.push(input.value);
<!-- use array method to sort the digits -->
array.sort(input.value)
<!-- using loop to print the values in array to the page -->
for(let i = 0; i < array.length; i++){
    dispaly.innerHTML = array[i]
}





